{"title":"澳门吟欢庆澳门回归","authors":["顾浩"],"dates":[{"year":1999,"month":12,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"澳门吟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢庆澳门回归"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顾浩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四百春秋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少日月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往事不堪回顾！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"殿高宫深难经雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丢了庄严国土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赢来狼舞！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孤舟一叶风浪里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟岸在、欲济无橹！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"归心昼夜系神州，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望尽天涯路！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九霄雷霆万钧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华夏崛起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"游子泪涨五湖！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"数代企盼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三生追求，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今朝梦圆愿如！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举双手再拜："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邓公构想耀千古！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更喜看："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳当空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莲花遍地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前程似画图！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}